{"tid":1034984,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇斯克查：我啲利物浦朋友每一季都話今季會贏英超","createTime":"2019-02-24T10:22:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T12:58:29.000Z","uid":147522,"like":60,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fe80f29add70b9fffffd781704cb3e203570b156","tid":1034984,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T10:22:17.000Z","msg":"曼聯英超大戰利物浦前，出名Nice嘅蘇斯克查無端端「寸王上身」，出口術向「紅軍」施壓之餘，仲乘機寸爆死敵英超無冠，認真抵死！蘇斯克查表示：「利物浦肯定會感受到爭標壓力，球迷感受到、球員亦都一樣，我哋都幾年冇贏過英超，當然想重溫好夢。英超真係好難贏，可能係世界上最難贏嘅錦標，我喺挪威有好多利物浦球迷朋友，佢哋每一季都話『今季會贏英超』，但每次去到10月份就會話『好，下季係我哋』。利物浦依家向住冠軍進發，聯賽最後衝刺肯定好刺激，不過我哋只需要專心做好自己嘅事。」"},{"pid":"695ddfb888ec8f4fad0b298bf70d25ff1595d34c","tid":1034984,"uid":2040,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T10:25:59.000Z","msg":"咁能串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91aa4d5e6dcaf78501e8a899d91ababbe2635c09","tid":1034984,"uid":26953,"like":12,"dislike":27,"score":-15,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T10:27:15.000Z","msg":"咁岩既 我啲獌朋友每一季都話今季會贏英超"},{"pid":"173f45ae0d935682ddb6ee31613d06a3bb8adc99","tid":1034984,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T10:27:18.000Z","msg":"蘇逼咁搶口想幫利拎英超？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4d14afe65171a34f6c2d0308aa3f0cde790c9c1","tid":1034984,"uid":153114,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T10:27:38.000Z","msg":"朋友=連登利迷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1546291a5c9bf5cbe2f4a9a29fe6cb1ec2324673","tid":1034984,"uid":147522,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T10:28:00.000Z","msg":"佢哋每一季都話『今季會贏英超』，但每次去到10月份就會話『好，下季係我哋』"},{"pid":"e04d110e7af9d63c856fc45494a53957133222ff","tid":1034984,"uid":21398,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"1546291a5c9bf5cbe2f4